Dialogue: 2,0:03:02.31,0:03:07.75,OP BR,,0,0,0,,Para onde a resposta levará? Procure!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:07.75,0:03:09.42,OP BR,,0,0,0,,Onde está a minha alma?
